                  , on the 5th of November, about the hour of seven in the night, and stealing two linen sheets, value twenty shillings, and four linen shirts, value forty shillings, the property of 
                     <persName id="t17751206-70-person1018">
                        Josiah
                         Harrop
                     <interp inst="t17751206-70-person1018" type="surname" value="Harrop"></interp>
